<lb ed="C I" n="0229b19"/>那羅延神王</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c01"/><p id="pI01p0229c0101">妙<note n="0229001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08073;＝旨【史】</note><app n="0229001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08073;</rdg></app>幽微。非聖無以盡於源。聖行之興。非
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c02"/>福智莊嚴。豈能弘其道。然今合邑諸人等。
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c03"/>宿殖<note n="0229002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30601;＝明【史】</note><app n="0229002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30601;</rdg></app>珠。久歷諸佛。故能異心同<note n="0229003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31068;＝契【史】</note><app n="0229003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">契</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31068;</rdg></app>。仰慕
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c04"/>遺蹤。在於定光像<note n="0229004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31069;＝前【史】</note><app n="0229004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">前</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31069;</rdg></app>。敬造七佛寶堪。并二
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c05"/>菩薩。賢聖諸僧。<note n="0229005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02793;＝彌【史】</note><app n="0229005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02793;</rdg></app><note n="0229006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31171;＝勒【史】</note><app n="0229006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31171;</rdg></app>下生。梵王帝釋。舍利
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c06"/>非<note n="0229007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31172;＝壹【史】</note><app n="0229007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">壹</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31172;</rdg></app>。其<note n="0229008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30645;＝金【史】</note><app n="0229008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app>容赫弈。照曜三千。<note n="0229009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31070;＝華【史】</note><app n="0229009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">華</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31070;</rdg></app>麗二相。妙
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c07"/>菀八十。剋木圖<note n="0229010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00410;＝泥【史】</note><app n="0229010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">泥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00410;</rdg></app>。像而非喻。採壁模形。焉
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c08"/>是其譬。睹之者淨信開<app source="0229002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30601;</rdg></app>。虔禮者三鄣殄
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c09"/>息。斯乃塵勞之中。紹如來種。籍此勝<note n="0229011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13224;＝善【史】</note><app n="0229011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13224;</rdg></app>。仰
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c10"/>願國祚永隆。三寶增盛。法界四生。七世先
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c11"/>靈。存<note n="0229012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15601;＝亡【史】</note><app n="0229012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15601;</rdg></app>父母。現在眷屬。發菩提心。<app source="0229005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02793;</rdg></app><app source="0229006" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31171;</rdg></app>下
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c12"/>生。甯偏伬滿C開化群迷。廣修万行。共集<app source="0229011" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13224;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c13"/>根。同證菩提之道。刊銘頌曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c14"/>法性如如。非有非<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>。體非分別。妙用非虛。
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c15"/>八相成道。似同凡夫。生而非生。滅而非滅。
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c16"/>神通隱顯。摩王歸軼。化導三千。人天獨步。
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c17"/>改迷接聖。慈悲覺<note n="0229013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00322;＝寤【史】</note><app n="0229013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00322;</rdg></app>。示三空門。令遊正路。
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c18"/>淨修波若。四攝資助。奮翼道品。菩提永固。
<lb ed="C I" n="0229c19"/>　　天統三年歲次丁亥三月壬申朔十五日丙戊建</p>
</div2>
